OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fquickly die out this evening. Then
OL,7,Fturning cloudier with rain spreading
OL,8,Fin from the west during the early
OL,9,Fhours, this occasionally heavy for
OL,10,FDumfries and Galloway.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA cloudy morning with
OL,13,Foccasional heavy rain at first.
OL,14,FShowers will develop for the
OL,15,Fafternoon, some possibly heavy with
OL,16,Fthe odd rumble of thunder in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
