OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FVariable amounts of cloud with showers
OL,7,For a few longer spells of rain,
OL,8,Fparticularly across western areas.
OL,9,FWarmer than of late, particularly in
OL,10,Fdrier, sunnier conditions in the east.
